## Attribution

This project uses data from:

- **ESA Climate Change Initiative (CCI) Fire_cci project**
  - Data: ESA Fire_cci Burned Area Grid product v5.1
  - Source: https://climate.esa.int/en/projects/fire/
  - License: ESA data policy applies
  
- **CEDA (Centre for Environmental Data Analysis)**
  - Archive: CEDA Data Archive
  - Source: https://catalogue.ceda.ac.uk/
  - License: CEDA data licensing terms apply

